The fantasy is always much
better than the reality.

497
00:26:35,886 --> 00:26:37,887
You think this is a joke?
That's my son.

498
00:26:37,972 --> 00:26:42,475
He's dying, and not one of you seem
to have the slightest clue why.

499
00:26:42,559 --> 00:26:45,728
I know. That's why
it's so interesting.

500
00:26:49,817 --> 00:26:52,360
Fever, stomach pain, seizures,

501
00:26:52,444 --> 00:26:56,281
peritoneal and subdural fluid
collection and now spots.

502
00:26:56,365 --> 00:26:58,408
Could be an allergic
reaction to one of his meds.

503
00:26:58,492 --> 00:27:01,286
That suddenly developed eight
hours after he started the meds?

504
00:27:01,370 --> 00:27:03,663
If it's not cancer or infection,
it has to be autoimmune.

505
00:27:03,747 --> 00:27:06,207
Systemic lupus complicated
by a CNS vasculitis

506
00:27:06,292 --> 00:27:08,960
would explain the rash,
fever, ascites...

507
00:27:09,044 --> 00:27:11,879
CNS vasculitis would cause a stiff
neck along with the headache.

508
00:27:11,964 --> 00:27:14,757
And would've showed up
on the dural biopsy.

509
00:27:15,426 --> 00:27:18,928
What about polyarteritis nodosa?
It can occur in kids.

510
00:27:19,013 --> 00:27:21,723
Except you can't have arteritis
without inflammation.

511
00:27:21,807 --> 00:27:24,559
Okay, you come up
with something better.

512
00:27:27,021 --> 00:27:28,104
Go on.

513
00:27:28,188 --> 00:27:30,064
There was some inflammation
in the skin biopsy.

514
00:27:30,149 --> 00:27:33,067
Plus he's got elevated
diastolic pressure.

515
00:27:33,152 --> 00:27:34,610
It's barely elevated,

516
00:27:34,695 --> 00:27:37,215
which you'd expect given the number
of procedures he's undergone.

517
00:27:37,239 --> 00:27:39,907
Well, barely is more
than not barely.

518
00:27:43,537 --> 00:27:45,204
Not my decision.

519
00:27:46,373 --> 00:27:48,666
But if it was, I'd say
start him on prednisone

520
00:27:48,751 --> 00:27:50,752
and get a testicular biopsy.

521
00:27:51,086 --> 00:27:53,526
If he's gonna have any real
inflammation, it'll be down there.

522
00:27:53,547 --> 00:27:54,630
Cameron and I will do it.

523
00:27:54,715 --> 00:27:56,799
