her back, or because Foreman does?

647
00:36:20,929 --> 00:36:22,763
Why would I care
what Foreman wants?

648
00:36:22,848 --> 00:36:25,599
Because you're not as big a
jerk as everyone thinks.

649
00:36:25,684 --> 00:36:26,684
Yes, I am.

650
00:36:26,768 --> 00:36:28,102
