659
00:36:47,581 --> 00:36:49,456
So you did it for you?

660
00:36:49,541 --> 00:36:51,500
I'm not the one
in charge any more.

661
00:36:51,585 --> 00:36:53,586
So you did it for Foreman?

662
00:36:53,670 --> 00:36:57,381
She's a smoking-hot,
newly-single bisexual.

663
00:36:57,465 --> 00:37:00,217
Why don't you just admit that
you like having her around?

664
00:37:00,302 --> 00:37:01,927
She's good for you.
You need her.

665
00:37:02,012 --> 00:37:05,639
Because I was born with a
heart three sizes too small.

666
00:37:06,224 --> 00:37:08,392
No, you weren't. Yes, I...

