00:37:10,812 --> 00:37:11,812
What?

668
00:37:27,370 --> 00:37:28,787
He still alive?

669
00:37:28,872 --> 00:37:30,039
Yeah.

670
00:37:30,248 --> 00:37:34,043
Good. Start him on heparin
and IV immunoglobulin.

671
00:37:34,127 --> 00:37:35,711
