because of Degos.

678
00:37:48,391 --> 00:37:51,352
Means it's primary
antiphospholipid syndrome.

679
00:37:53,355 --> 00:37:55,230
Are you sure? Nope.

680
00:37:56,107 --> 00:38:00,027
But I will be if he responds to
the heparin and immunoglobulin.

681
00:38:05,367 --> 00:38:06,951
By the way,

682
00:38:07,035 --> 00:38:09,119
someone screwed
over your girlfriend,

683
00:38:09,204 --> 00:38:12,706
and she ran to me, Cuddy, and
Wilson, everyone but you.

684
00:38:14,751 --> 00:38:16,543
She's not over you.

685
00:38:17,253 --> 00:38:18,629
Or she is.

686
00:38:48,118 --> 00:38:49,576
Where did you find it?

687
00:38:49,661 --> 00:38:50,744
Find what?

688
00:38:51,913 --> 00:38:54,665
Niacin-bound
chromium supplements.

689
00:38:55,333 --> 00:38:58,502
