You don't know about it?

690
00:38:58,586 --> 00:39:00,587
No, been here all night.

691
00:39:01,506 --> 00:39:04,508
One of Dibala's previous docs was
prescribing ultra-high doses

692
00:39:04,592 --> 00:39:07,261
