between the HDL numbers.

696
00:39:13,560 --> 00:39:16,228
We're safe. We're covered.

697
00:39:18,273 --> 00:39:20,274
You really didn't
request the info?

698
00:39:21,109 --> 00:39:22,693
No.

699
00:39:22,777 --> 00:39:25,112
And obviously
you didn't either,

700
00:39:26,614 --> 00:39:28,157
which means...

701
00:40:03,193 --> 00:40:04,651
It worked.

702
00:40:05,236 --> 00:40:06,987
The medicine worked.

703
00:40:08,198 --> 00:40:09,573
It worked.

704
00:40:25,006 --> 00:40:26,840
