705
00:40:29,594 --> 00:40:31,345
Fat, old, black guy.

706
00:40:32,055 --> 00:40:35,557
I knew he had to be taking
something for his cholesterol.

707
00:40:35,642 --> 00:40:37,142
And what now?

708
00:40:38,019 --> 00:40:39,853
I'm not the boss.

709
00:40:39,938 --> 00:40:41,688
You don't think
I should be fired?

710
00:40:41,773 --> 00:40:42,940
Why?

711
00:40:43,024 --> 00:40:46,693
I doubt we'll ever be treating
a genocidal dictator again.

712
00:40:47,320 --> 00:40:49,863
Better a murder
than a misdiagnosis.

713
00:40:54,244 --> 00:40:56,995
Whether you want to be
in charge or not,

714
00:40:57,747 --> 00:40:59,123
you are.

715
00:41:00,125 --> 00:41:02,042
And you always will be.

716
00:41:19,978 --> 00:41:22,813
75-year-old African
man presented to our hospital

717
00:41:22,897 --> 00:41:25,691
following a rapid
onset of hemoptysis.

718
00:41:25,775 --> 00:41:27,860
He had been fine
prior to onset.

719
00:41:27,944 --> 00:41:31,155
No chest pain, fever,
coughing or chills.

720
00:41:31,906 --> 00:41:34,867
He does note a
nine-hour plane flight...

